attributes.description: Asian Energy Services Ltd is an oilfield service and reservoir imaging company, offering a suite of geophysical services specializing in land and well seismic services and operation and maintenance services for oilfields.[1] It is one of the few companies providing end-to-end services in the upstream oil segment.[2]
